datalog_actions:
can_access(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'admin'), isEq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, 'false'), not deny_access(S, R).
deny_access(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'admin'), isEq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, 'false').
can_write(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'admin').

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, admin) :- Subject(S).
has_isMeeting(S, false) :- Subject(S).
datalog_actions: can_access(S, O, read) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, admin), has_isMeeting(S, false).
can_access(S, O, write) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, admin).
can_write(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "admin").

can_access(U, R, "read") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin").
can_access(U, R, "write") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin").
can_read(U, R) :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin"), not_in_meeting(U).
can_access(S, O, "write") :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "admin").
can_access(S, O, read) :- Subject(S), Object(O), not role(S, admin), isMeeting(S, false).

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, "admin") :- Subject(S).
not_equal_subject_resource_user(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_access(S, R, "read") :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "admin"), not_equal_subject_resource_user(S, R).
can_read(S, O) :- Admin(S), PaperReviewContentRatingRC(O).
can_access(S, R, "read") :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "admin"). can_access(S, R, "write") :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "admin").
can_access(U, R, "read") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin"), not_in_meeting(U).
can_access(S, O, "read") :- Subject(S), Object(O).
can_read(S) :- Subject(S), not role(S, "false").
can_access(S, A) :- Subject(S), role(S, R), R = "admin", (A = "read" ; A = "write").
can_access(U, R, "read") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin"). can_access(U, R, "write") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin").
can_access(S, O, A) :- Subject(S), Object(O), Action(A), not is_conflicted(S).

xacml:
<Policy PolicyId="RPSlist.20.0.0.2.4" RuleCombiningAlgId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:rule-combining-algorithm:first-applicable">
                        <Target>
                            <Subjects>
<Subject>
    <SubjectMatch MatchId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:function:string-equal">
        <AttributeValue DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">admin</AttributeValue>
        <SubjectAttributeDesignator SubjectCategory="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:subject-category:access-subject" AttributeId="role" DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
    </SubjectMatch>
    <SubjectMatch MatchId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:function:string-equal">
        <AttributeValue DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">false</AttributeValue>
        <SubjectAttributeDesignator SubjectCategory="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:subject-category:access-subject" AttributeId="isConflicted" DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
    </SubjectMatch>
</Subject>
                            </Subjects>
                            <Actions>
<Action>
    <ActionMatch MatchId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:function:string-equal">
        <AttributeValue DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">read</AttributeValue>
        <ActionAttributeDesignator AttributeId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:action:action-id" DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
    </ActionMatch>
</Action>
                            </Actions>
                        </Target>
                        <Rule Effect="Permit" RuleId="RPSlist.20.0.0.2.4.r.4">
                            <Target>
<Resources>
    <Resource>
        <ResourceMatch MatchId="urn:oasis:names:tc:xacml:1.0:function:string-equal">
            <AttributeValue DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">ismeetingflag_rc</AttributeValue>
            <ResourceAttributeDesignator AttributeId="isSeeUnassignedAllowed" DataType="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
        </ResourceMatch>
    </Resource>
</Resources>
                            </Target>
                        </Rule>
                    </Policy>
datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, "admin") :- Subject(S).
not_conflicted(S) :- Subject(S).
has_attribute(R, "ismeetingflag_rc") :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_access(S, R, "read") :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "admin"), not_conflicted(S), has_attribute(R, "ismeetingflag_rc").
can_access(S, A) :- Subject(S), action(A, "read").
can_access(S, O, 'read') :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'admin'), has_isMeeting(S, 'false').
deny_all :- false.

datalog_relationships:
role(S, 'false') :- Subject(S).
isConflicted(S, 'false') :- Subject(S).
subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, 'admin') :- Subject(S).
hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, 'false') :- Subject(S).
datalog_actions: can_access(S, R, 'read') :- Subject(S), Resource(R), role(S, 'false'), isConflicted(S, 'false'), subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, 'admin'), hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, 'false').
can_access(U, R) :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, 'admin').
deny_access(S) :- Subject(S), isConflicted(S).
can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'admin'), is_resource(R, 'ismeetingflag_rc').
can_access(S, Action) :- Subject(S), Action(Action), role(S, "false"), (Action = "read"; Action = "write").
